# Frontend Conventions

- **No heavy business logic in components** — use Zustand stores (`app/store/`) and feature `*Api.js` files.
- **All HTTP** through `lib/apiClient.js` and feature-level APIs (`bookApi.js`, `chapterApi.js`, `aiApi.js`).
- **Tailwind only** for styling; reuse shadcn `components/ui/`.
- **TipTap**: single reusable `RichTextEditor.jsx` wrapper; extensions colocated under `components/Editor/` as needed.
- Routes in `app/routes.jsx`; shell layout in `components/Layout/`.
